<div style="font-family: sans-serif; max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; line-height: 1.6; color: #333;">
  <h2 style="color: #2563eb;">Password Reset Request</h2>

  <p>Hi <%= @resource.email %>,</p>

  <p>Someone has requested a link to change your password for your <strong><%= Rails.configuration.x.app_name %></strong> account. You can do this through the link below:</p>

  <p style="text-align: center; margin: 30px 0;">
    <%= link_to 'Change my password', edit_password_url(@resource, reset_password_token: @token), 
        style: "background-color: #2563eb; color: white; padding: 12px 24px; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 5px; font-weight: bold; display: inline-block;" %>
  </p>

  <p>If you didn't request this, please ignore this email.</p>
  <p>Your password won't change until you access the link above and create a new one.</p>

  <hr style="border: 0; border-top: 1px solid #eee; margin: 30px 0;">

  <p style="font-size: 0.8em; color: #999; text-align: center;">
    &copy; <%= Time.current.year %> <%= Rails.configuration.x.app_name %>. All rights reserved.
  </p>
</div>
